"""
AgentOS Unified CLI - 统一命令行入口

Usage:
    agentrt <command> [options] [arguments]

Commands:
    Service Management:
        service list              List all services
        service start [name]      Start service(s)
        service stop [name]       Stop service(s)
        service restart [name]    Restart service(s)
        service status [name]     Get service status
        service health            Health check all services

    Agent Management:
        agent list                List registered agents
        agent register <name>     Register new agent
        agent start <id>          Start agent
        agent stop <id>           Stop agent
        agent info <id>           Get agent details

    Task Management:
        task list                 List tasks
        task submit <desc>        Submit new task
        task status <id>          Get task status
        task cancel <id>          Cancel task
        task result <id>          Get task result

    Protocol Operations:
        protocol list                  List all protocol adapters
        protocol info <proto>          Show detailed protocol information
        protocol test <proto>          Test protocol connectivity
        protocol detect                Detect protocol from input content
        protocol send <proto> <method> [params]  Send a protocol message
        protocol stats                 Show protocol statistics
        protocol transform <src> <tgt> [data]   Transform between protocols
        protocol capabilities <proto>  Show protocol capabilities

    Configuration:
        config get <key>          Get configuration value
        config set <key> <value>  Set configuration value
        config list               List all configuration
        config reload             Reload configuration

    Monitoring:
        monitor metrics           Show metrics
        monitor alerts            Show active alerts
        monitor dashboard         Open Grafana dashboard

    Development:
        dev init                  Initialize development environment
        dev build                 Build project
        dev test                  Run tests
        dev doctor                Run diagnostics
        dev shell                 Open development shell

    System:
        version                   Show version
        status                    Show system status
        help                      Show help

    Database:
        db migrate [--target=v2]  Run heapstore schema migration
        db migrate-status         Show migration status
        db migrate-rollback       Rollback to previous schema version
        db backup                 Create data backup
"""

